                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d639">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-05-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 2, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Great Britain has accepted guarantee by Salvador of payment of indemnity by
                    Nicaragua in London within a fortnight; and so soon as Nicaragua accepts and so
                    informs British admiral he is instructed to leave Corinto.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bayard</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
